Fake intelligence has been the watchword since the first days of the Bush (41) administration, when the neocons now creeping back into Washington behind their stealth candidate, Trump, tried first to burn down the world. In Washington, unconfirmed but probable President Elect Trump has surrounded himself, with the exception of National Security Advisor Mike Flynn, with Russia haters. Leading the list is Congressman Mike Pompeo who is slated to head the CIA. Pompeo, with a razor thin CV, believes defeating ISIS can only be accomplished by invading Iran, who he insists is their primary supporter. With strategic analytical capabilities like this, terrorism could have no better friend than Pompeo at CIA. With Georgia's Israeli backed move against Russia in 2008, the new "axis of evil" in the region, Ukraine, Turkey and Georgia are likely to target Armenia and offer it to the US as a base of operations for Trump's proposed invasion of Iran, cornerstone of his planned upcoming regional war in Asia. From F. William Engdahl, an assessment that cannot be ignored: "I state clearly my conviction, and please recall this as Trump Presidency policies unfold after January 20, 2017 to see if I am correct or not: Donald Trump was put into office to prepare America for war, a war the banks of Wall Street and the US military industrial complex are not presently in a position economically or industrially or otherwise, geopolitically, to win. His job will be to reposition the United States for them to reverse the trend to disintegration of American global hegemony, to, as the Dick Cheney, Paul Wolfowitz Project for the New American Century put it in their September, 2000 report, "rebuild America's defenses." To do that preparation, a deception strategy that will fatally weaken the developing deep bonds between Russia and China will be priority. It's already begun. We have a friendly phone call from The Donald to Vladimir the Fearsome in Moscow. Russian media is euphoric about a new era in US-Russia relations after Obama. Then suddenly we hear the war-mongering NATO head, Stoltenberg, suddenly purr soothing words to Russia. Float the idea that California Congressman and Putin acquaintance, Dana Rohrabacher, is leaked as a possible Secretary of State. It's classic Kissinger Balance of Power geopolitics-seem to ally with the weaker of two mortal enemies, Russia, to isolate the stronger, China. Turkey has also been involved in Ukraine and Turkish "Grey Wolves," government sanctioned terror groups, have been deployed to threaten Crimea, this done during the supposed "rewarming" of relations between Ankara and Moscow. Sources report that Trump sent his son, Donald Jr., to meet with Turkish representatives to discuss joint operations against Iran and that Erdogan's announcement scrapping his deal with Russia is a direct result of that Paris meeting. All this occurred only 24 hours after Tehran announced a warming in relations with Turkey, a new diplomatic initiative that lasted one day. Naucnici otkrili koji je tacan odgovor na vecito pitanje Posted date: mart 18, 2018In: ZIVOT Naucnici Univerziteta Sefild i Varvik su, cini se, nasli odogovor na pitanje svih pitanja: sta je starije, kokoska ili jaje, pise britanski Dejli Mejl. Na najcesce postavljeno pitanje od postanke sveta, ljudi u najvecem broju odgovaraju "jaje", uz objasnjenje da su na taj nacin jos dinosaurusi dolazili na svet. Medutim, naucnici sa univerziteta Sefild i Varvik imaju drugaciji odgovor. Njihovo istrazivanje, naime, pokazalo je da ljuska kokosjeg jajeta moze nastati samo iz proteina koji se stvara u jajnicima kokosi, sto znaci da je kokos morala postojati pre jajeta. Taj protein, objasnjavaju naucnici, zove se OC-17 i deluje poput katalizatora koji ubrzava razvoj ljuske, a tvrda ljuska je potrebna da zastiti zumance u kojem se razvija pile Naucnici su u istrazivanju koristili superkompjuter HECToR kako bi mogli da zumiraju unutrasnjost jajeta i prate njegov razvoj. Ono sto su otkrili je da je protein OC-17 kljucan za podsticanje kristalizacije u ranim stadijumima razvoja ljuske tako sto pretvara kalcijum karbonat u kristale kalcita koji prave ljusku. Kristali kalcita se, inace, mogu naci u kostima i oklopima raznih zivotinja, s tim da se kod kokosaka on stvara brze nego kod bilo koje druge vrste i proizvodi sest grama ljuske u 24 sata. Deflagratia a avut loc la trecerea unui vehicul militar in care se aflau soldati turci. Zona de sud-est a Turciei este lovita de cateva luni de un val de violente odata cu intensificarea confruntarilor intre fortele turce si rebelii separatisti kurzi. Un acord de incetare a focului intre armata turca si Partidul Muncitorilor din Kurdistan (PKK) a fost incalcat in iulie anul trecut, pe fondul acuzatiilor reciproce in urma stagnarii negocierilor de pace. Peste 40.000 de persoane au murit in conflict dupa ce PKK a inceput insurectia armata, in 1984. PKK, care sustine ca lupta pentru autonomia kurzilor din regiune, este considerata organizatie terorista de catre Turcia, Uniunea Europeana si SUA. Incepand din luna iunie a anului trecut, in Turcia s-au inregistrat mai multe atacuri cu bomba, unele fiind revendicate de gruparea jihadista Stat Islamic, potrivit autoritatilor de la Ankara. Na Zemlji, duzina dana meri se rotacijom planete oko svoje ose, a duzina godine kruznim kretanjem oko Sunca. Ono sto je interesantno, a sto do sada nije bilo primeceno, jeste da za zvezde na ekstremnim periferijama galaksija "jedna godina" traje oko milijardu godina. Za nase Sunce, jedna rotacija oko sredine nase galaksije Mlecni put traje oko 225 do 250 miliona godina, tako da rotacija nije ista za sva tela, a zavisi od njihove udaljenosti od centra. Vodeci naucnik istrazivanja Gerhard Meurer rekao je da je otkrice o ujednacenom rotiranju galaksija "prilicno cudno". "Pomislio sam da je to prilicno cudno. Male i velike galaksije - sve rotiraju za isto vreme", rekao je profesor Meurer iz Medunarodnog centra za radijska astronomska istrazivanja, prenela je agencija AAP. Istrazivaci su pronasli i dokaze o tome da se starije zvezde nalaze blize ivicama galaksija, iako se ocekivalo da se tu nadu novoformirane zvezde i gas. Prema dosadasnjim teorijama, galaksije se razvijaju duze vreme i postepeno se sire, pri cemu starije zvezde zauzimaju mesto blize centru diska. Meurer je rekao da ce ovo otkrice pomoci astronomima da shvate gde se galaksije zavrsavaju, i da vise ne gube vreme i procesorsku moc kompjutera na oblasti izvan njihovih ivica.
